{
  "stem": "8784.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Schindler was-- which had all the similarities of a-- of a camp like Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Schindler would occasionally mill around us and talk about it, how good we will have it in that camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at one time, I remember him making a comment that the reason for the barbed wires and the watchtowers in this concentration camp is that not because of fear that we would be escaping from there, but he thinks that we will have it so good in this concentration camp that people from the outside might want to come into the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's the reason for the barbed wire and the watchtowers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And shortly after the completion of this concentration camp-- this still would have been in 1943, maybe-- maybe summer of 1943 or fall of '43-- we began life in-- in his concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the plan had included, by that time, that 1,000 people would work in this concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the workforce was changing rapidly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "From 100 people, it became 300 and 700.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and quickly 1,000 people were in this concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this-- our life took on an entirely different picture.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was no longer this fearful, bestial kind of camp that we were in in Krakow-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was the kind of a camp that we worked during the hours of working in the Krakow-- in the Emalia and then would walk out through the gate from the factory into the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we-- it was rather peaceful inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We did not see too many German SS guards coming in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Or if they came in, it was on very rare occasions.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
